description:
The fourth and fifth sets of correction parameters Ap and Bp are expressed by parameters {circumflex over (α)}, P, and Q. The fourth set of the correction parameters Ap and Bp is

Ap=√{square root over (P)}−j{circumflex over (α)}√{square root over (Q)}

Bp=−{circumflex over (α)}√{square root over (P)}−j√{square root over (Q)}, 

and the fifth set of the correction parameters Ap and Bp is

Ap=√{square root over (P)}+j{circumflex over (α)}√{square root over (Q)}

Bp=−{circumflex over (α)}√{square root over (P)}+j√{square root over (Q)},
